            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Learn about the Clean Water Act. Make notes on when it was passed, its environmental goals, what progress has been made and what remains to be done to achieve the law's goals. Describe the impact, benefits, and costs of the law as well as what is required to implement and enforce the law."
