          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Determine five ways to conserve resources or use resources more efficiently in your home, school, or camp. Practice at least two of these methods for at least one week."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "10 Ways to Take Care of the Environment (video)",
