            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "12617",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Identify five items in your household that will become hazardous waste. Explain how they should be properly stored, what special care is needed for disposal, and proper disposal options available in your area."
