          "value": " In your community or camp, investigate two invasive plant or animal species. Learn where the species originated, how they were transported to this ecosystem, their life history, how they are spread, how they impact the native ecosystem, and the recommended means to eradicate or control their spread. Discuss what you learned with your counselor."
